title: Stuff 4 Multiples Twin Baby Journal, Orange (Discontinued by Manufacturer)
description: With this twin baby journal by Stuff 4 Multiples, you'll be able to clearly see when you last fed your twins, how many diapers your twins went through, how long and when your twins slept, as well as record those all important (but easy to forget) firsts. Most importantly with this twin baby journal, you don't have to remember a thing except of course, where you last left it.
